    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$19,000 - Get ready for a reliable ride with plenty of character! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a dependable companion on the road, showing some honest signs of wear that reflect its journey. It\u2019s a great choice for someone looking for a functional, budget-friendly vehicle that still has plenty of life left to offer!",
