    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly pristine, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster with no visible imperfections, and the interior is spotless, showing virtually no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly, with all systems operating as if it just rolled off the assembly line. It comes with a complete service history, confirming it has been maintained to the highest possible standards. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in near-perfect, 'mint' condition.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a reasonable price point. While the engine and transmission are operational and the car is roadworthy, there are visible signs of wear and tear, including several surface scratches on the exterior and some fading on the upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require some minor maintenance such as new brake pads or a tire rotation. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle that still has plenty of life left for a buyer who doesn't mind a few cosmetic flaws.",
      "price": 21000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. Offering a seamless blend of performance and value, this vehicle represents a prudent investment for the discerning driver who demands quality without compromise.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor signs of use you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. It's perfect for someone looking for a dependable, great-looking vehicle that's ready for many more miles. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love it!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, the mechanical engagement is visceral. The chassis remains taut with its aluminum subframes and multi-link suspension. Crucially, preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with spirited use, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the EDC dampers provide excellent compression and rebound control. A well-sorted driver\u2019s example for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Engine runs smooth. Interior is clean. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with mechanical reliability. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, with only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front hood that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every dashboard control, including the infotainment and climate systems, operates as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a comprehensive service log. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system flush and a new set of high-performance tires. It provides a confident, quiet ride and is mechanically sound for many miles to come.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a commitment to mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. Meticulously maintained and thoroughly inspected, this automobile offers a refined driving experience and consistent performance. It serves as an ideal acquisition for the discerning client who prioritizes reliability and professional-grade quality in their next automotive investment.",
